1 The top five most overrated women on the WWE roster (no numbers, as they are equally overrated in their own ways) are:
Shayna Baszler
Ruby Riott
Sonya Deville
Lana
Nia Jax


2. Crock Lesnar may be a nice person away from the WWE, but he needs to just go away. No one wants him around anymore.

4. Paul Heyman needs to just been "the Authority figure" and no longer have say in how things are run.


5. There is no making Bobby Lashley relevant happening ever again. He did it to himself.
